org.mobicents.slee.container.profile
Interface ProfileConcrete

All Superinterfaces:
javax.slee.profile.Profile, javax.slee.profile.ProfileManagement
public interface ProfileConcrete
extends javax.slee.profile.Profile, javax.slee.profile.ProfileManagement

Start time:16:51:13 2009-03-13
Project: mobicents-jainslee-server-core
Profile object interface which declares extra management methods to store some runtime properties. This interface represents actual object that has local copy of profile data. Its logical counter part is SbbEntity+SbbConcrete. We can have multiple object representing SbbE cached data, with this object it is similar with this. However we cant use instance of this classes as ProfileEntities, since they MUST act ass concrete impl (see how SbbConcrete is used inside SbbObject)

Author:
Bartosz Baranowski , Alexandre Mendonca
